These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, tiparillo, vegafina, ritmeester
House: cape-cod, craftsman, townhouse, ranch-style
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, r&b, trance
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the craftsman house is the prince-smoker##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the fan of r&b is the cape-cod house##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the craftsman house##1
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
6. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the craftsman house is the owner of the cat##1
8. the fan of house is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar         | prince  | ritmeester  | tiparillo | vegafina |
| House           | craftsman | cape-cod | ranch-style  | townhouse  |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | r&b      | country | house      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

