.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, pall-mall, tiparillo, blend
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, magic-tricks, photography, woodworking
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the blend-smoker is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the tiparillo-smoker##1
7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola       | iced-tea | tea        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| Cigar   | tiparillo      | pall-mall       | blend     | game    |
| Hobby         | photography | woodworking | rock-climbing | magic-tricks |

