.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, collecting, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, musical, scientific
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, bus, airplane, tram
 1. the person drinking tea is the person driving the tram##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up       | tea        | mirinda        |
| Hobby           | dancing   | collecting | board-games   | hiking |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | horror    | scientific | musical        |
| Transport           | airplane         | subway  | tram       | bus         |

