.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, firefighter, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, sports, comedy, crime
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, pall-mall, swisher, dannemann
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, guinea-pig, horse
