2. the firefighter is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the scientist is on the right of the bartender##1
8. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | engineer   | bartender  | scientist | firefighter |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | crime       | sports       | adventure     |
| Cigar   | swisher       | dannemann    | pall-mall     | oliveros  |
| Pet           | ferret     | guinea-pig | horse     | cat         |

