4. the indian is on the left of the french##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the alhambra-smoker is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| City           | edinburgh  | rome    | liverpool | hamburg |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | romance    | drama         | superhero    |
| Nationality   | indian   | french     | thai          | turkish      |
| Cigar         | bolivar | swisher | alhambra      | game      |

