 2. the person eating banana is the indian##1
 3. the accountant is the polish##1
 4. the fan of hip-hop is the person eating banana##1
 5. the russian is the writer##1
 6. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 8. the polish is on the right of the russian##1
 9. the doctor is on the far left##1
10. the fan of classical is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
