.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, may, september
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, sudoku, woodworking
There 4 different types of food: apricot, kiwi, lime, corn
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, scooter, taxi
 1. the person eating apricot is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the person eating apricot is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday    | june | february     | may    | september |
| Hobby       | baking | sudoku    | woodworking | cooking |
| Food         | kiwi   | lime  | corn        | apricot    |
| Transport   | taxi   | quad-bike | airplane    | scooter |

