3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who growsbegonia##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
9. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | video-games | baking     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | coffee       | lemonade       | almond-milk  |
